OL,3,CMan, 45, found guilty of murdering mum
OL,4,Cand hiding her body under sofa
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering 31-year-old mum after she
OL,8,Fwas last seen entering his flat in
OL,9,FStafford.
OL,11,FWayne Bond, 45, killed Rebecca
OL,12,F(Beckii) Simkin and hid her body under
OL,13,Fan upturned sofa. He failed to alert
OL,14,Femergency services for several days
OL,15,Fand did not give evidence during his
OL,16,Ftrial.
OL,18,FThe pair were captured on CCTV walking
OL,19,Ftogether on Newport Road, Stafford, at
OL,20,Faround 7:40pm on 23 July 2024.
