OL,6,FMs Simkin could be clearly seen
OL,7,Fwithout any injuries, police said.
OL,9,FLater that night, at 9:15pm, footage
OL,10,Fshowed them entering Bond's flat at
OL,11,FEagle House - a supported
OL,12,Faccommodation site for adults facing
OL,13,Fhomelessness.
OL,15,FBeckii, who did not live there, was
OL,16,Fsigned in but never signed out. She
OL,17,Fwas not seen on any CCTV after that
OL,18,Fpoint.
