OL,3,CMan, 45, found guilty of murdering mum
OL,4,Cand hiding her body under sofa
OL,6,FSeveral residents reported hearing a
OL,7,Fwoman screaming late on 25 July and in
OL,8,Fthe early hours of 26 July.
OL,10,FOn 29 July, Bond returned to the flat
OL,11,Fand told a member of staff that a
OL,12,Fwoman who had been staying with him
OL,13,Fhad died, claiming they had a
OL,14,F"squabble".
OL,16,FParamedics were called and Beckii was
OL,17,Ffound dead, wrapped in a blanket
OL,18,Fbeneath a sofa. Bond was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder.
