OL,3,CMan, 45, found guilty of murdering mum
OL,4,Cand hiding her body under sofa
OL,6,FFollowing a 10-day trial at Stafford
OL,7,FCrown Court, Bond was found guilty by
OL,8,Fa jury on Tuesday. He is due to be
OL,9,Fsentenced on Friday.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Beckii's mother and
OL,12,Fstepfather, Julie and Michael Riglar,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Beckii was an amazing mum and
OL,14,Floving daughter. Beckii had her faults
OL,15,Fbut she never deserved to die this
OL,16,Fway."
