OL,4,Cand hiding her body under sofa
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Gina Pope, from
OL,7,FStaffordshire Police's Major
OL,8,FInvestigations Department, said:
OL,9,F"Beckii was tragically subjected to a
OL,10,Fviolent assault which sadly led to her
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,F"Bond showed absolute cowardice in
OL,14,Ffailing to report Beckii's death and
OL,15,Fleaving her in his flat for a number
OL,16,Fof days - and for failing to give
OL,17,Fevidence during the trial."
